{"tid":1515526,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【焯焯有餘】林鄭製造經濟災難 - 關焯照","createTime":"2019-08-29T07:46:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T11:37:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"4adce9d144760e5538ad0671313c7cefed3e7cf0","tid":1515526,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:46:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20190829/20757884\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190829%2F20757884&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRvLVWyXx0XMfrvcdwhNvS5Y%3D&h=aa472473\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190829%2F20757884&h=65dee264\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20190829/20757884</a><br />\n<br />\n【焯焯有餘】林鄭製造經濟災難 - 關焯照<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190829/large/1567006255_e2a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190829%2Flarge%2F1567006255_e2a2.jpg&h=19c73c30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭如果使用《緊急法》來止暴制亂，香港肯定玩完，內地經濟也會被拖累。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一份本地報章專欄引述政府消息，一旦反送中運動不斷升級或令警員或示威者出現嚴重傷亡，林鄭會考慮使用《緊急法》來止暴制亂。如果成事，林鄭肯定是瘋了，她準備以核彈炸曱甴，香港和內地經濟要做陪葬品了。<br />\n<br />\n香港能夠成為金融中心是外資對香港的制度和政府管治有信心，但特首竟然考慮不跟遊戲規則，使用《緊急法》來個一鑊熟，這又怎會令外資會對香港這個金融中心有信心呢！所謂《緊急法》是賦予特首差不多無限權力，可以拉人封艇、凍結資產，甚至加重量刑。總之，這法例是將一把刀架在每一位香港人的頭上。<br />\n<br />\n如果你是外國投資者，又怎會將自己置身險境，所以當《緊急法》推出時，香港的金融中心便會即時玩完，因為大量資金會離開香港，屆時聯滙制度也會崩潰，香港經濟會出現前所未見的大衰退。香港玩完，內地經濟也會被拖累，因為中國的唯一金融中心已被《緊急法》所摧毀，內地金融開放也即時玩完，內地經濟所面對的震盪亦難以估計。人民幣滙價必會急挫，跌幾多，天曉得！<br />\n<br />\n哈佛大學教授Carmen Reinhart幾天前對外國傳媒表示，香港政局可能引發全球經濟衰退，筆者本也不太相信，但現在，筆者不能不稱讚這位哈佛教授有先見之明。<br />\n<br />\n關焯照<br />\n經濟學家<br />\n本欄逢周四刊出 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n【何車500】聯想候52周低位吸納 (何車)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【魚樂無窮】月供股票的關鍵 (唐牛)"},{"pid":"94f780c5c052deef0581c2a47d003f18fb27bc30","tid":1515526,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:46:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0DhhYaU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0DhhYaU.jpg&h=54caa31d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2562664ce43fa2ee74b4569704d054da702353ce","tid":1515526,"uid":19743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:47:05.000Z","msg":"唔好意思<br />\n借個位黎<br />\n香港人撐香港隊<br />\n入場向世界表達訴求<br />\n賽前有奏鄰國國歌儀式，大家識做!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x2WiF8C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx2WiF8C.jpg&h=29888ad2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/goQjqOR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgoQjqOR.jpg&h=8f2b904e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JhMKBVv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJhMKBVv.jpg&h=385dcf42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1487629/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1487629/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"dd779dfab333e8a5969f236c9a66d9099e5df864","tid":1515526,"uid":37869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:49:47.000Z","msg":"究竟呢招係中共指使<br />\n定係呢隻豬隊友諗出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc95356afa41fdfbc306209c770dd64295783453","tid":1515526,"uid":19676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dd779dfab333e8a5969f236c9a66d9099e5df864","tid":1515526,"uid":37869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:49:47.000Z","msg":"究竟呢招係中共指使<br />\n定係呢隻豬隊友諗出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T08:11:03.000Z","msg":"大陸佬點會<br />\n一定係條八婆以為自己好醒"},{"pid":"c4038b99692519d0ae7ecaedc1cc57a0cf7660ec","tid":1515526,"uid":137569,"like":2,"dislike":0,"scor